Name: hostscli
Version: 1.0.3
Summary: hostscli is a CLI tool to block / unblock websites using /etc/hosts
Home-page: https://github.com/dhilipsiva/hostscli
Author: dhilipsiva
Author-email: dhilipsiva@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: HostsCLI Docs
        =============
        
        A CLI tool to block / unblock websites using /etc/hosts. Super simple and easily extendable.
        
        
